# Typography Guidelines

## Font System

- **Sentient**: Serif font for headings (`font-heading`, `font-sentient`)
- **Geist Sans**: Primary sans-serif font (`font-sans`)
- **Geist Mono**: Monospace font (`font-mono`)

## Usage

```tsx
// Headings
<h2 className="font-heading font-bold text-2xl">Heading</h2>

// Body text
<p className="font-sans">Regular text</p>

// Sentient variations
<p className="font-sentient font-light">Light Sentient</p>
<p className="font-sentient font-light italic">Light Italic</p>
<p className="font-sentient font-bold">Bold Sentient</p>

// Code
<code className="font-mono">code</code>
```

## Font Configuration

- All fonts configured in `lib/fonts.ts`
- Font files in `public/assets/fonts/sentient-light/`
- Font family settings in `tailwind.config.ts`

## Best Practices

- Use appropriate font for context (headings, body, code)
- Maintain consistent typography throughout the app
- Use standard Tailwind classes for weight and style